      "text": "\u2022 Hero number animates in\n  (.contentTransition(.numericText))\n\u2022 Tier badge color+shape+symbol\n\u2022 L2 footer becomes visible\n\u2022 L3 link \"Is this estimate for me?\"\n  becomes reachable\n\u2022 WeatherKit lockup visible\n\u2022 Success haptic (.sensoryFeedback)\n\u2022 Lands on NowView (= Main Screen\n  below, in LANE 2)",
