      "strokeColor": "#666666",
      "text": "Severity = color + shape + SF Symbol + label  (AAA contrast, color-blind safe).  Range mapping:  \u2265240 = Long (\"240+ min\" cap),  60-239 = Long,  20-59 = Moderate,  &lt;20 = Short.",
