      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "When elapsed \u2265 original estimate:  hero swaps to \ud83d\udee1 \"Estimated window elapsed. Cover up, reapply, or move to shade.\"\nSingle warning haptic.  Button: \"Recalculate\" (.borderedProminent).  This is the safety-critical moment \u2014 must NOT be quiet.\nOn every recalculate, the L1 footer + L3 link remain visible \u2014 photosensitizers re-encounter the disclaimer surface.",
