    {
      "id": "mpcd9ydlekr5d9n0l9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 475,
      "y": 1555,
      "strokeColor": "#BF360C",
      "text": "\ud83d\udea8 L1 STICKY + PHOTO-SENS REACH-BACK",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "version": 1,
      "width": 288,
      "height": 18,
      "angle": 0,
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 526620650,
      "versionNonce": 185039746,
      "index": null,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779179062089,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\ud83d\udea8 L1 STICKY + PHOTO-SENS REACH-BACK",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true,
      "customData": null,
      "baseline": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd9ydlw7ipxxqdu5f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 475,
      "y": 1580,
      "strokeColor": "#333333",
      "text": "L1 modal re-fires every cold launch\n(Donatello M1).  NO \"Don't Show Again.\"\n\nThe L1 surface is NOT load-bearing alone\nfor the high-risk persona (Accutane/lupus):\nthey modal-blind on cold launch & need to\nreach the photo-sens caveat mid-task.\n\n\u2192 L3 link on verdict card is additive\n   (deep-links to L4 `notForMe`).\n\u2192 Footer \u24d8 About is also tappable.\n\nD-2026-05-19-007 + D-2026-05-19-011.\nSkill: persona-keyed-disclaimer-visibility.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "version": 1,
      "width": 283,
      "height": 210,
      "angle": 0,
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1243534606,
      "versionNonce": 1817328039,
      "index": null,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779179062089,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "L1 modal re-fires every cold launch\n(Donatello M1).  NO \"Don't Show Again.\"\n\nThe L1 surface is NOT load-bearing alone\nfor the high-risk persona (Accutane/lupus):\nthey modal-blind on cold launch & need to\nreach the photo-sens caveat mid-task.\n\n\u2192 L3 link on verdict card is additive\n   (deep-links to L4 `notForMe`).\n\u2192 Footer \u24d8 About is also tappable.\n\nD-2026-05-19-007 + D-2026-05-19-011.\nSkill: persona-keyed-disclaimer-visibility.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
