      "seed": 1204636876,
      "versionNonce": 1457064028,
      "index": null,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779179062089,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\ud83d\udccc  240-MINUTE DISPLAY CAP",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true,
      "customData": null,
      "baseline": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcd9ydmv0wmutvqq3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 875,
      "y": 1580,
      "strokeColor": "#333333",
      "text": "If model output \u2265 240 minutes, the hero\nDISPLAYS \"240+ min\" (= \"4+ hours\") rather\nthan the literal integer.\n\nWHY:  Fitz V/VI + SPF 70 + low UV can yield\n\"480 min\" \u2014 mathematically right but\nbehaviorally misleading (implies a literal\n8-hour safe stretch, which the model is\nnot validated to claim).\n\nInternal calculation is unchanged. Display\nclamp only. VoiceOver mirrors the cap.\n\nSource: Suchi \u00a71.8 \u2192 Linka spec \u00a73.3.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "version": 1,
      "width": 283,
      "height": 210,
      "angle": 0,
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 157404122,
      "versionNonce": 2018231313,
      "index": null,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779179062090,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "If model output \u2265 240 minutes, the hero\nDISPLAYS \"240+ min\" (= \"4+ hours\") rather\nthan the literal integer.\n\nWHY:  Fitz V/VI + SPF 70 + low UV can yield\n\"480 min\" \u2014 mathematically right but\nbehaviorally misleading (implies a literal\n8-hour safe stretch, which the model is\nnot validated to claim).\n\nInternal calculation is unchanged. Display\nclamp only. VoiceOver mirrors the cap.\n\nSource: Suchi \u00a71.8 \u2192 Linka spec \u00a73.3.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true,
      "customData": null,
      "baseline": 9
