      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Apple's WeatherKit T&C requires the\n\" Weather\" lockup wherever data is shown,\n+ tappable link to\nweatherkit.apple.com/legal-attribution.html\n\nSurfaces:\n  \u00b7 Below verdict card on NowView (always)\n  \u00b7 Full lockup in About \u2192 Weather data\n  \u00b7 Dedicated AttributionView screen\n\n\u274c REMOVE Open-Meteo CC BY 4.0 footer\n   from all iOS surfaces (web keeps it).\n\nD-2026-05-19-002/003/004 \u2014 launch BLOCKER\nif missing. Apple review will reject.",
