    {
      "id": "mpcdatioez8aqnmhojc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 75,
      "y": 1810,
      "strokeColor": "#333333",
      "text": "Suchi-named L3 pattern. Inline link on verdict\ncard; deep-links to AboutView with anchor =\n`notForMe`. Uses ScrollViewReader.proxy.scrollTo\nwith .animation(.smooth) \u2014 honors Reduce Motion.\n\nVoiceOver label MUST spell out the destination:\n\"Is this estimate for me? Opens About,\nconditions and medications that may affect\nthis estimate.\"\n\nNOT a way to soften L1. NOT a \"Don't Show\nAgain\" loophole. ADDITIVE to L1, not a replacement.\n\nPersona served: Accutane, lupus, vitiligo,\nalbinism, pregnancy, post-procedure cohort.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "version": 1,
      "width": 336,
      "height": 225,
      "angle": 0,
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 866610596,
      "versionNonce": 1390659637,
      "index": null,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779179102448,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Suchi-named L3 pattern. Inline link on verdict\ncard; deep-links to AboutView with anchor =\n`notForMe`. Uses ScrollViewReader.proxy.scrollTo\nwith .animation(.smooth) \u2014 honors Reduce Motion.\n\nVoiceOver label MUST spell out the destination:\n\"Is this estimate for me? Opens About,\nconditions and medications that may affect\nthis estimate.\"\n\nNOT a way to soften L1. NOT a \"Don't Show\nAgain\" loophole. ADDITIVE to L1, not a replacement.\n\nPersona served: Accutane, lupus, vitiligo,\nalbinism, pregnancy, post-procedure cohort.",
