      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Eight items Plunder wants attorney sign-off\non before App Store submit (don't block design):\n\n 1. NCBI citation wording in About\n 2. \"Apple Weather\" vs \" Weather\" body prose\n 3. L1 modal final copy (Donatello M1 verbatim?)\n 4. L3 link copy: \"Is this estimate for me?\"\n 5. SPF chip neutrality (no \"recommended\" badge)\n 6. Privacy paragraph wording\n 7. Pricing claim: \"no subscription ever\"\n 8. Banned phrases audit (port from prototype JS)\n\nSurfaces affected:  L1 modal, verdict card,\nSkinTypeView footer, AboutView all sections,\nAttributionView, App Store description.",
