    {
      "id": "mpcdatioszvi0jqxq1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 875,
      "y": 1810,
      "strokeColor": "#333333",
      "text": "When elapsed \u2265 original estimate:\n  \u00b7 Hero swaps to \ud83d\udee1 + caption\n  \u00b7 ONE warning haptic\n  \u00b7 \"Recalculate\" button (re-fetches UV)\n  \u00b7 L2 footer STILL VISIBLE\n  \u00b7 L3 link STILL TAPPABLE\n\nThis is the photosensitizer re-attestation\nmoment \u2014 not a modal re-fire, but a\nreturn-to-disclaimer-surface moment.\n\nAsha (Accutane persona): her body has\nalready burned at 5 min while watering\nplants. The window-elapsed UI must NOT be\nquiet \u2014 but also must NOT moralize.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "version": 1,
      "width": 277,
      "height": 225,
      "angle": 0,
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "roundness": null,
