      "type": "text",
      "x": 1680,
      "y": 145,
      "strokeColor": "#333333",
      "text": "Screen fills (LANE 1):\n  \u2591 light gray   = neutral system screen (splash, verdict)\n  \u2591 red          = L1 disclaimer (mandatory acknowledgment)\n  \u2591 light blue   = system task screen (Fitz, location)\n  \u2591 yellow       = passive moment (no separate screen)\n  \u2591 green        = success / first verdict landing\n\nSub-regions (LANE 2 \u2014 Main Screen):\n  \u2591 green        = verdict card / hero\n  \u2591 light blue   = inputs + timer\n  \u2591 purple       = WeatherKit attribution\n  \u2591 orange       = window-elapsed / re-attestation\n  \u2591 gray         = L2 footer (inert)\n  \u2591 pink         = Settings/About entry \u2192 L4 anchor\n\nArrows:  solid blue = primary linear flow\n         solid orange = annotation pointer\n         (no dashed arrows used in this diagram)",
      "fontSize": 12,
