      "type": "text",
      "x": 735,
      "y": 2295,
      "strokeColor": "#B71C1C",
      "text": "\u26a0 BRANCH: planning\nat home in Feb. No\ncurrent useful location.\nDenied \u2192 graceful\nempty state. v1 has\nno \"plan-for-elsewhere\"\naffordance (v1.1).",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "version": 1,
