      "type": "text",
      "x": 475,
      "y": 2495,
      "strokeColor": "#E65100",
      "text": "\u26a0 UNDER-PICK RISK\nActually Fitz IV. Self-narrative\n\"I tan, I don't burn\" may push\nhim to Type V/VI. Behavior-first\nrow copy is PARTIAL mitigation \u2014\nhe reads \"rarely burns\" on V and\nself-selects on that clause alone.",
